data.description:
Welcome to your new sanctuary! Nestled on just over 3 acres in the heart of Vadnais Heights, this 4-bedroom, 2-bath home with a 3-car garage is the perfect blend of spacious living and cozy comfort. Imagine unwinding in the open living area, where a warm fireplace and sleek hard floors create the perfect backdrop for both lively gatherings and quiet evenings in.

The heart of this home is its kitchen, outfitted with a smart fridge and shiny new stainless steel appliances - a dream for anyone who loves to cook or entertain. The main floor bathroom has been beautifully updated, adding a touch of modern luxury to your daily routine.

Step outside and you'll find more than just a yard; it's your own private escape. Relax in the hot tub, enjoy the bounty from your own cherry and apple trees, and take in the tranquility that comes with living at the end of a quiet street. With a new roof, a newer furnace, and the luxury of endless water, this home is as practical as it is charming.
